items.details: Non-GMO corn. Gluten free. 60 calories per cup. Certified gluten free. Whole grain: 15 g or more per serving. Eat 48 g or more of whole grains daily. WholeGrainsCouncil.org. Organic non-GMO corn. Air popped. No trans fat. No MSG. Vegetarian friendly. Whole grain. Not treated with growth hormones. The FDA claims that no significant difference has been shown between milk derived from rBST-treated and non-rBST treated cows. www.popartsnacks.com. facebook.com/popartsnacks. twitter.com/popartsnacks. Popcorn is the canvas that we paint with bold flavor! Like the pop art movement itself, Pop Art Gourmet Popcorn transforms the ordinary into the extraordinary. We elevate this all-American snack by infusing it with fun flavors that appeal to the foodie snack lover. Our palette of ingredients includes only the finest quality organic non-GMO popcorn and all natural herbs and spices. Our White Cheddar Jalapeno Popcorn has the fiery flavor of jalapeno peppers combined with the smooth and creamy taste of white cheddar cheese. Those that crave a little heat will enjoy this scrumptious south of the boarder creation. We pop when you pop. We don't shine, if you don't shine is a motivating phrase for us at Pop Art Snacks and has inspired our We Pop when you Pop Charity Campaign. At Pop Art Snacks, we are committed to helping charities pop by giving a portion of our profits to causes that you feel are doing amazing and necessary work in the world. For more information and to submit your favorite charity for review please go to: www.popartsnacks.com/charities. Made in the USA.

I loved it as a kid, and that didn't change when I grew up and trained at Le Cordon Bleu in London.
